node.text: You asked. We delivered. Strawberry Lager is now available year-round!

node.text:
We've got a new pilot brew on tap! Come stop by the taproom today to try Brewer TJ's Hefe. It's a German style wheat beer with a 6.2% ABV... It would make him smile if you tried it out 😂

#abita #abitabeer #abitabrewing #abitabrewingcompany  #craftbeer #brewery #beer #beerstagram #beerlover #cultureontap #louisianatrue #pilotbrew #brewer
